      "content": "that's a great start, love the atmosphere. to make it feel even more real for the reader, i want to add some people into the scene. can you describe the types of people you'd see hanging out on these street corners or loitering in the shadows? i want to capture that specific vibe of the 'dangerous' elements that make this neighborhood so intimidating.",
